*** Settings ***
Documentation    Login Page keywords.
Resource         ../common.resource

*** Variables ***
${LOGIN_URL}         ${BASE_URL}/
${WELCOME_MESSAGE}   id:inventory_container

*** Keywords ***
Navigate To Login Page
    [Documentation]    Open the login page and wait for it to be ready.
    Go To                           ${LOGIN_URL}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${USERNAME_FIELD}    ${TIMEOUT}

Enter Username
    [Arguments]    ${username}
    Wait And Input Text    ${USERNAME_FIELD}    ${username}

Enter Password
    [Arguments]    ${password}
    Wait And Input Text    ${PASSWORD_FIELD}    ${password}

Click Login Button
    Wait And Click Element    ${LOGIN_BUTTON}

Login With Credentials
    [Documentation]    Fill both fields and click Login.
    [Arguments]    ${username}    ${password}
    Enter Username         ${username}
    Enter Password         ${password}
    Click Login Button

Verify Login Error Message
    [Documentation]    Assert that the error banner contains ${expected_message}.
    [Arguments]    ${expected_message}
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Contain           ${ERROR_MESSAGE}    ${expected_message}

Verify Successful Login
    [Documentation]    Assert that we were routed to the post-login page.
    Wait Until Element Is Visible    ${WELCOME_MESSAGE}    ${TIMEOUT}
    Element Should Be Visible        ${WELCOME_MESSAGE}
